Description: Bluetooth HID keyboard and mouse sharing
 Share your keyboard and mouse with other devices over Bluetooth.
 Works with Mac, Windows, Android, and other Bluetooth HID hosts.
 .
 Features:
  - Share keyboard and mouse input over Bluetooth
  - Exclusive input capture (input doesn't affect host system while sharing)
  - Simple GUI with one-click sharing
  - Emergency stop: Press Left Shift + Space + Right Shift simultaneously
